{"tid":1156420,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"日記分享 - 「經歷」","createTime":"2019-05-15T15:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T17:08:26.000Z","uid":202912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"baf999557156395e586d826246a2d6e0e1080aa7","tid":1156420,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:04:56.000Z","msg":"「經歷」<br />\n很少會回想起兩三天、三四天前發生的事，但也許會突然記起某天的一個時刻，總之就是某個的日子，偶然的片段。不會有明確的數字觀念讓你意識到是隔了多少的時間、日子，最多是「這個月裏」、「幾個月前」或「上年的時候」。經歷過的，唯有印象深刻的，或偶然觸動了你的神經的才能被記起、被意識到。也許我曾與某個路邊行乞的人交換過眼神，也許小時候曾有誰摸過我的頭？自身實際經歷過的，有甚麼，是甚麼，注定被遺忘的又如何能找回。但哪能執着？社會上更多是活在當下，熱情地去迎接未來的人。唯有你，仍執着於不明不白的記憶之中。"},{"pid":"65b9f403649fb9b5fc03af31277b407144ea2153","tid":1156420,"uid":202912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661cf9dc96a159a1a8d07550b18a9d0877b7f003","tid":1156420,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf1bfde366e77f28c2366ecd751826bffb02df6","tid":1156420,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"要沉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38f6d7d7761f3c819c35d861461fb0415363931","tid":1156420,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;The past beats inside me like a second heart.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0be6ef8f20182a99521a13026b5a718f156cad77","tid":1156420,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:08:26.000Z","msg":"goodnight world"}]}